<h1>Shuttle Private Bus Service Guatemala Antigua</h1><p>&nbsp;Casa Xelajú provides safe and reliable private shuttle services throughout Guatemala, offering convenient transportation options from Quetzaltenango (Xela) to popular destinations such as Lake Atitlán, Panajachel, Antigua, Chichicastenango, and La Aurora International Airport in Guatemala City. Since 1987, the company has built a strong reputation for dependable service, catering to tourists, business travelers, and students seeking comfort, safety, and flexibility in their travel plans.</p>
<p>&nbsp;Whether traveling alone, with family, or in a group, Casa Xelajú offers comfortable vehicles that can accommodate between three and twenty-five passengers. Each trip is designed to ensure a smooth and stress-free journey, with flexible pickup and drop-off times that can be tailored to individual itineraries. Bilingual staff are available to assist international travelers and make the experience as easy and enjoyable as possible.</p>
<p>&nbsp;Casa Xelajú operates daily departures from Quetzaltenango to destinations including Antigua, Panajachel, Lake Atitlán, and Guatemala City, as well as return routes to Xela. The company also provides 24-hour service at La Aurora International Airport to meet the needs of arriving or departing travelers. With consistently high customer satisfaction and years of trusted experience, Casa Xelajú continues to be a preferred choice for transportation in Guatemala.</p>
<p>&nbsp;For those needing to stay overnight in Guatemala City, Casa Xelajú can arrange a homestay with a local family. Guests enjoy a continental breakfast before being driven directly to the first-class bus station, ensuring a comfortable and seamless transfer. Upon arrival at the Quetzaltenango bus station, the company provides direct transportation to the traveler’s final destination.</p>
<p>&nbsp;The fleet includes private cars for up to three passengers and minibuses for groups of nine to twenty-five. Casa Xelajú’s service is ideal for travelers planning routes such as Antigua to Xela, Airport to Xela, Xela to Panajachel, Xela to IRTRA, Xela to Antigua, Xela to Airport, Panajachel to Xela, Antigua to Airport, Xela to Las Georginas, Panajachel to Airport, and Xela to Chichicastenango.</p>
<p>&nbsp;With nearly four decades of experience, English-speaking staff, and a focus on comfort and reliability, Casa Xelajú remains one of the most trusted names in private transportation across Guatemala. Whether you are catching a flight, heading to a weekend getaway at Lake Atitlán, or exploring the country’s cultural centers, Casa Xelajú ensures a safe, efficient, and professional travel experience.</p><a href="https://www.casaxelaju.com/shuttle-service-private-transportation-guatemala/"><b><span style="font-size: x-large;">Shuttle Private Bus Service Guatemala Antigua</span></b></a><br />
